channel.title: RealPK F2P PKing
channel.description:
[img]http://realpk.info/img/banner.png[/img]
Features: 100% real time pking. staking has been taken out completely. 30X exp rate + prayer/magic are easy to level up. Custom, fun formulae everyone will love. DDoS protected dedicated from Staminus.
and much more!
Drags:
[img]http://img101.imageshack.us/img101/3943/drags.png[/img]
training spot:
[img]http://img246.imageshack.us/img246/4057/traina.png[/img]
Custom DM area that we're building:
[img]http://img297.imageshack.us/img297/9503/dmarena.png[/img]
We are in it for the long run and hope you come and join us!
Check my signature for the link!
